{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"10d57bdf25","title":"杂文——团支书争鸣","origin":"《关于“野草”、“蜜蜂”社反动小集团的材料》，中共中央民族学院整风办公室编，1957年12月。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c1df20c341","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":3,"articleId":"10d57bdf25"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"1007c7f41e","name":"李鹤亭"},{"id":"6dd61a6c39","name":"中央民族学院"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"f5c0651e42","type":"title","text":"杂文——团支书争鸣","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"10d57bdf25"},{"id":"67938ec824","type":"authors","text":"中央民族学院李鹤亭","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"10d57bdf25"},{"id":"880ece5ab3","type":"subtitle","text":"（李鹤亭：中央民族学院语文系一年级藏语班学生）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"10d57bdf25"},{"id":"c4d02325ef","type":"subtitle","text":"团支书争鸣        白痴(李鹤亭)","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"10d57bdf25"},{"id":"c697aa219b","type":"paragraph","text":"支书：来!帮我一下，吾今天第一次写大字报。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"10d57bdf25"},{"id":"387723afc5","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：什么内容?","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"10d57bdf25"},{"id":"e8dc7abfb3","type":"paragraph","text":"支书：我念，你听。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"10d57bdf25"},{"id":"513f1aef9d","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：你念吧!我替你写。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"10d57bdf25"},{"id":"1c5c4857ef","type":"paragraph","text":"支书：“党是我头脑的创始者，也是千百万人的救主！！”","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"10d57bdf25"},{"id":"f425c2bc4b","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：这是什么意思？","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"10d57bdf25"},{"id":"a4ed2e7e81","type":"paragraph","text":"支书：含蓄，有力，充分说明我爱党。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"10d57bdf25"},{"id":"33047f9413","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：好!你再念？","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"10d57bdf25"},{"id":"f418090fc5","type":"paragraph","text":"支书：“在党的教练和锤培下，我甜密的活到现在。”","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"10d57bdf25"},{"id":"b23f9696be","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：这你争什么鸣呢？","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"10d57bdf25"},{"id":"ca9fc881e8","type":"paragraph","text":"支书：鸣我心内的赤诚吗?你听这最后两句更有力：“我保证，在不久的将来，我将摇身一变，成为一个神圣的共产党员?”","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"10d57bdf25"},{"id":"faa87b4d70","type":"appellation","text":"(录自“野草”第3期)","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"10d57bdf25"},{"id":"07b086d164","type":"subtitle","text":"渣滓    春回(李鹤亭)","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"10d57bdf25"},{"id":"761244f50d","type":"paragraph","text":"王影摇(此处一字打不出)着肥大的身躯，来回的走动，爬满怒须的油光闪闪的脸上，开始流着汗，“同志们！”他停了下来，向围在四周的几个人扫了一眼：“我们必须立即动手，否则我们便会失败!”","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"10d57bdf25"},{"id":"ebcf167fcf","type":"paragraph","text":"“我说，支书……”一个瘦子向他弓了弓腰，“我认为：要达到我们的目的，第一步我们要缓和矛盾，抓住群众!”","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"10d57bdf25"},{"id":"04b5058b74","type":"paragraph","text":"王影的头猛然抖了一下，肥胖的脸朝着瘦子：“你说的很对，我也这样想，其他的人还有意见吗?”他又向大家扬了扬脸。","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"10d57bdf25"},{"id":"c75506b940","type":"paragraph","text":"“我说，”一个带眼镜的青年说：“我不同意这样作，帮助党搞好整风，揭发内部矛盾，这是好事情，既然我们党员已经落在群众后边了，那我们就应该赶上去!”","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"10d57bdf25"},{"id":"67ec789222","type":"paragraph","text":"“行了?”王影厉声的说，“我们是党员，是整风之对象，现在群众已闹得这么厉害，请什么高教部民委会来，同志们!现在我们应该懂得缓和矛盾!”","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"10d57bdf25"},{"id":"8e67709f96","type":"paragraph","text":"刚才说话的那个瘦子又蹭了几步到王影面前：“支书，还有几个团的干部可以为我们作些事，他们都正在要求入党。”","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"10d57bdf25"},{"id":"f748b65d32","type":"paragraph","text":"“哫……”王影责备的眼光扫了他一眼，瘦子退了下来，他知道这些话不应当在这里说。","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"10d57bdf25"},{"id":"cea990097f","type":"paragraph","text":"王影提了提胖大的脾部，坐了下来，脸上还继续流着汗。","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"10d57bdf25"},{"id":"242e80f1fe","type":"paragraph","text":" (录自“野草”第3期)","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"10d57bdf25"},{"id":"2ae6a46efa","type":"subtitle","text":"为了我    茅竹(李鹤亭)","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"10d57bdf25"},{"id":"1b50225dd5","type":"paragraph","text":"“哈哈……哈…”李催扶着肥胖的嘴巴大笑着，谁知什么事使他这么快乐，汗珠顺脸上滚着，两条乱眉笑的也几乎要飞起来。","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"10d57bdf25"},{"id":"1e0f692644","type":"paragraph","text":"他旁边站着一个高个儿青年，脸上带着喜色，“老李啊，咱们的好时候到了!”","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"10d57bdf25"},{"id":"4cd5c919d9","type":"paragraph","text":"“哈哈!是呀，我们的好时候来了”，他脸上的笑纹像一条条黑色的绳索，两只眼睛眯起来，闪着一种似笑非笑的清冷的光辉，“哼！我们报复的时候到了，早几天，那群落后分子一个劲给我提意见，现在也该让我们整他们了!”","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"10d57bdf25"},{"id":"da68e3dd15","type":"paragraph","text":"他不惜用最恶毒的语言咒骂着：“这群右派分子，反党分子。”“那么我那个事怎么办?”青年人焦急的问他：“这学期我是不是能入上党?”","index":30,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"10d57bdf25"},{"id":"cf66cbc6dd","type":"paragraph","text":"“哎！别慌吗!这又不是我一个人当家，这个学期你做得很有成绩，我已经把情况汇报上去了。”","index":31,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"10d57bdf25"},{"id":"edabfe8733","type":"paragraph","text":"“希望你今后继续努力，向那些人继续战斗，尽量庇护我。”青年人点了头。","index":32,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"10d57bdf25"},{"id":"fb6d8e3e4c","type":"paragraph","text":"“你一定能入上的”，他笑着赏赐的拍了拍青年的肩膀“干吧!为了我，为了你入党。”","index":33,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"10d57bdf25"},{"id":"a444f3cbc1","type":"paragraph","text":" (录自“野草”第4期，6月20日)","index":34,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"10d57bdf25"}],"page":{"id":"ae8c336933","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"10d57bdf25","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}